    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a serious project or a source for parts. The engine is currently non-operational and will require a complete overhaul or replacement to get back on the road. The body has significant rust patches, multiple dents, and the clear coat is peeling extensively across most panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily torn, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are no longer functioning. It will need to be towed from its current location.",
