    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle is offered in impeccable, showroom-grade condition, reflecting a history of fastidious maintenance and climate-controlled storage. The exterior finish remains flawless, complemented by an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Engineered for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of the marque. We invite rigorous inspection to confirm its status as a benchmark of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
