      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting flawless exterior surfaces and a pristine, meticulously preserved interior. Mechanically, the unit is indistinguishable from new, having undergone a comprehensive technical evaluation to ensure absolute operational integrity. For the discerning buyer who demands peerless quality and a documented history of care, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unparalleled caliber.",
      "price": 48500.0,
