    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute dream of a car! Honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it\u2019s been totally babied and is in pristine shape. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or smudge on this beauty; it's practically flawless inside and out. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to fall in love at first sight!",
      "price": 43900.0,
