    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2001 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Laguna Seca Blue. This example is powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline, mated to a precise Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is superlative: the VANOS unit has been professionally overhauled, and the rod bearing service is documented. The chassis is structurally perfect with preventative subframe reinforcement already completed. Every aspect of the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, providing the telepathic handling these M-cars are known for. This is a blue-chip investment for the discerning enthusiast seeking a turn-key, high-performance icon.",
